      <div class="msgContentFrame">You can replace it by clicking light thrust, then clicking heavy thrust, and equip in main hand.  <br /> <br />I dont recommend this for a permenent thing though. Heavy thrust is significantly lower DPS ( higher stamina cost). I tend to use heavy thrust solo on green mobs and easy yellow mobs, and pretty much 100% of the time in groups. I use Light Thrust on tougher yellow mobs and all orange and red mobs that I solo. I generally use pierce during leves. </div>
